00:27:46,624 --> 00:27:51,212
Haakon Haakonsson, kau harus istirahat.

212
00:28:04,017 --> 00:28:05,101
Kau lapar?

213
00:28:07,061 --> 00:28:08,563
Tidak, terima kasih.

214
00:28:09,939 --> 00:28:11,107
Kau yakin?

215
00:28:12,901 --> 00:28:14,569
Bisa kuambil satu.

216
00:28:16,779 --> 00:28:19,407
Kau tahu jika memberi jari kelingking,

217
00:28:19,574 --> 00:28:20,867
akan kuambil seluruh hidangan.

218
00:28:35,506 --> 00:28:38,009
Boleh kucoba?
/ Ya.

219
00:28:39,677 --> 00:28:40,678
Bukan begitu.

220
00:28:41,554 --> 00:28:43,473
Kau harus seperti ini.

221
00:28:44,432 --> 00:28:46,851
Jika Bagle datang ke arahmu,
lakukan seperti ini.

222
00:28:49,437 --> 00:28:50,438
Siap.

223
00:28:51,439 --> 00:28:54,692
Bagus. Ya, seperti itu.
Sabet kakinya.

