01:00:31,129 --> 01:00:32,338
Ya, ya, ya.

489
01:00:36,008 --> 01:00:37,927
Frikk, tetap pegangi dia.

490
01:00:39,512 --> 01:00:41,597
Kau sudah siap?
/ Tidak!

491
01:00:58,698 --> 01:01:00,241
Sudah selesai.

492
01:01:15,840 --> 01:01:16,841
Biar aku saja.

493
01:01:17,008 --> 01:01:19,510
Enak saja. Ingat apa
