01:05:24,171 --> 01:05:25,589
Kau kedatangan tamu.

523
01:05:40,980 --> 01:05:43,315
<i> Kenapa?
/ Aku takut.</i>

524
01:05:46,277 --> 01:05:49,530
<i>Aku tak tahan sendirian
