mengantarmu ke kamar.

526
01:05:58,289 --> 01:05:59,915
Nanti kutemui.

527
01:08:05,207 --> 01:08:06,458
Inge.

528
01:08:17,136 --> 01:08:20,139
Gisle! Keluarkan aku!

529
01:08:21,849 --> 01:08:23,851
Tidak!
/ Gisle!

530
01:08:30,983 --> 01:08:33,068
Selamat datang di peternakan!
Halo.

531
01:08:41,368 --> 01:08:43,120
Selamat datang di peternakan.

532
01:08:54,256 --> 01:08:57,343
Kita harus teruskan perjalanan.

533
01:08:57,509 --> 01:09:00,846
Torstein. Tenang dulu.

534
01:09:01,013 --> 01:09:03,557
Mana Haakon?
/ Dia tertidur.

535
01:09:08,771 --> 01:09:10,064
Torstein.

536
01:09:13,817 --> 01:09:14,985
Aku di sini.

537
01:09:35,172 --> 01:09:36,298
Minumlah.

538
01:09:40,969 --> 01:09:42,388
Minum lagi.

539
01:09:43,847 --> 01:09:45,766
Apa ini?
/ Minyak ikan.

540
01:09:45,933 --> 01:09:47,476
Kau membutuhkan nutrisi, Torstein.

541
01:09:47,643 --> 01:09:49,186
Ya, ya, ya.

542
01:09:57,736 --> 01:09:59,196
Sekarang giliranmu.

543
01:10:16,755 --> 01:10:18,716
Boleh tambah lagi?
/ Mau tambah?

544
01:10:19,633 --> 01:10:21,051
Terima kasih.

545
01:10:21,468 --> 01:10:22,678
Besulang.

546
01:10:47,828 --> 01:10:49,121
Apa ini?

547
01:10:49,288 --> 01:10:51,248
Kau sudah bilang perlu
orang-orang yang rela berperang.

548
01:10:51,415 --> 01:10:52,875
