645
01:25:14,360 --> 01:25:17,155
Egil! Bangun!
Kita harus pergi!

646
01:25:50,730 --> 01:25:51,814
Skjervald.

647
01:25:53,941 --> 01:25:55,151
Skjervald!

648
01:26:19,592 --> 01:26:22,220
Skjervald. Skjervald.

649
01:26:25,640 --> 01:26:26,974
Kau berhasil.

650
01:26:27,934 --> 01:26:29,102
Berhasil.

651
01:26:32,689 --> 01:26:34,023
