652
01:26:35,525 --> 01:26:38,945
Tapi pewaris tahta
harus tetap hidup.

653
01:28:06,532 --> 01:28:09,285
Semua  baik² saja.
Pergi sana.

654
01:28:11,996 --> 01:28:13,498
Jangan khawatir.

655
01:28:13,664 --> 01:28:15,082
Takkan ada pernikahan.

656
01:28:15,792 --> 01:28:18,002
Tapi jangan tunjukkan
rasa takutmu, Christina.

657
01:28:23,925 --> 01:28:28,137
